706465f-a.text:

Thomas Hunt house, later known as the Alexander E. Orr home. (Alexander
Ector Orr was at one time President of the New York Chamber of Commeroe,
and was also President of the New York Produce Exchange for several terms ).
It was demolished in 1934.
